t in", "start": 505.56, "duration": 3.64}, {"text": "these 10 stages and we made this little", "start": 507.4, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "kind of quiz thing where if you put in", "start": 509.2, "duration": 2.88}, {"text": "your business information, it'll tell", "start": 510.76, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "you where you're at and the most", "start": 512.08, "duration": 3.24}, {"text": "important part for you, what to do for", "start": 513.52, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "each of functions of the business across", "start": 515.32, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "product, marketing, sales, customer", "start": 516.56, "duration": 3.56}, {"text": "success, recruiting, IT, human resources", "start": 517.76, "duration": 4.44}, {"text": "and finance. And so, no matter what", "start": 520.12, "duration": 3.919}, {"text": "you're struggling with, someone else has", "start": 522.2, "duration": 3.84}, {"text": "already struggled with it and solved it.", "start": 524.039, "duration": 3.281}, {"text": "And so I'd like to give you this thing", "start": 526.04, "duration": 2.12}, {"text": "absolutely free. You can go to", "start": 527.32, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "acquisition.com/roadmap,", "start": 528.16, "duration": 3.24}, {"text": "plug in your business information, and", "start": 529.8, "duration": 3.76}, {"text": "if you want us to actually help you", "start": 531.4, "duration": 3.6}, {"text": "de-constrain the business and you're", "start": 533.56, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "trying to scale, we'd love to help you", "start": 535.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "out. On the thank you page you can book", "start": 536.6, "duration": 4.12}, {"text": "a call with my team and we will", "start": 538.0, "duration": 4.28}, {"text": "look at the business, see if we can", "start": 540.72, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "help, and if we can, we'll invite you", "start": 542.28, "duration": 3.08}, {"text": "out to Vegas and we'll do this in person", "start": 543.32, "duration": 4.76}, {"text": "live.", "start": 545.36, "duration": 2.72}]